mem_commutant_iff:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `exprℂ -/
@[simp]
theorem mem_commutant_iff {S : von_neumann_algebra H} {z : «expr →L[ ] » H (exprℂ) H} :
    z ∈ S.commutant ↔ ∀ g ∈ S, g * z = z * g :=
  iff.rfl
#align mem_commutant_iff mem_commutant_iff

@[simp]
theorem mem_carrier {S : von_neumann_algebra H} {x : «expr →L[ ] » H (exprℂ) H} :
    x ∈ S.carrier ↔ x ∈ (S : Set («expr →L[ ] » H (exprℂ) H)) :=
  iff.rfl
#align mem_carrier mem_carrier
ext:
@[ext]
theorem ext {S T : von_neumann_algebra H} (h : ∀ x, x ∈ S ↔ x ∈ T) : S = T :=
  SetLike.ext h
#align ext ext
commutant_commutant:
@[simp]
theorem commutant_commutant (S : von_neumann_algebra H) : S.commutant.commutant = S :=
  SetLike.coe_injective S.centralizer_centralizer'
#align commutant_commutant commutant_commutant
coe_commutant:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `exprℂ -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_commutant (S : von_neumann_algebra H) :
    ↑S.commutant = Set.centralizer (S : Set («expr →L[ ] » H (exprℂ) H)) :=
  rfl
#align coe_commutant coe_commutant
centralizer_centralizer:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →L[ ] » -/

theorem centralizer_centralizer (S : von_neumann_algebra H) :
